------ Ideal Workflow ------
Describe Image

---- Current Environment ------
Every component is a Docker container

1. Devmachine -- which is a centos7 image with git and RBTools. 
2. Jenkins -- Official Jenkins image with docker installed. 
3. Reviewboard (Reviewboard + memcache + mysql) 
4. sample node application.

----- Demo --------

prerequisites.

1. docker installed os with version 17.12.0-ce
2. docker-compose with verion 1.18.0
3. about 4 GB RAM
4. 10 GB disk

Note: This machine should be publicly available just to make it work with Github webhook. 